<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784706' id='t-784706'>the same magazine that had put us on that list</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789082' id='t-789082'>five years before.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791445' id='t-791445'>And as I'm sitting in the lobby
