<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794402' id='t-794402'>I notice there's a magazine copy</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796786' id='t-796786'>of the current issue right there on the table,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799405' id='t-799405'>and I pick it up, and I look at the headline</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801061' id='t-801061'>across the top, and it says,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='802826' id='t-802826'>&quot;America's Fattest Cities: Do You Live in One?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807507' id='t-807507'>Well, I knew I did,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='809652' id='t-809652'>so I picked up the magazine</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811804' id='t-811804'>and I began to look,</span>
