<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='817561' id='t-817561'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='823984' id='t-823984'>Then I looked on the list of fittest cities,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='826909' id='t-826909'>and we were on that list.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='829072' id='t-829072'>We were on the list as the 22nd
fittest city in the United States.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='832450' id='t-832450'>Our state health statistics are doing better.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835637' id='t-835637'>Granted, we have a long way to go.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='837749' id='t-837749'>Health is still not something</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='838888' id='t-838888'>that we should be proud of in Oklahoma City,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='840425' id='t-840425'>but we seem to have turned the cultural shift</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='844208' id='t-844208'>of making health a greater priority.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='847289' id='t-847289'>And we love the idea of the demographics</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='850132' id='t-850132'>of highly educated twentysomethings,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='851942' id='t-851942'>people with choices, choosing Oklahoma City</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='853711' id='t-853711'>in large numbers.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='855160' id='t-855160'>We have the lowest unemployment
