<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='891714' id='t-891714'>You've been a great audience and very attentive.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='893502' id='t-893502'>Thank you very much for having me here.</span>
